            , I saw him snatch of the shawl, the prisoner is the man that snatched it; I can swear to the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was going after a truss of hay, I heard some people hollowing out stop thief, a man stopped me as I was running along with the people; that is not the gentleman that stopped me. The gentleman here came up and asked me what was the matter.</p>
